Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for FORA TD-4251/U-RIGHT TD-4252/TD-4253/TD-4254 No-Coding Blood Glucose Monitoring System using electrochemical biosensor technology for blood glucose measurement
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from finger and alternative sites (palm, forearm, upper-arm, calf, thigh), for use by healthcare professionals and people with diabetes at home to monitor diabetes control; not for diagnosis or screening of diabetes or use on neonates.
